abstract: Data includes retail sales and leading economic indicators for June, and company reports will include Goldman Sachs, Coca-Cola, Bank of America, Google, Microsoft and General Electric.
snippet: Data includes retail sales and leading economic indicators for June, and company reports will include Goldman Sachs, Coca-Cola, Bank of America, Google, Microsoft and General Electric.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC DATA Data to be released this week includes retail sales for June and business inventories for May (Monday); the Consumer Price Index and industrial production for June (Tuesday); building permits for June and the Federal Reserve’s Beige Book (Wednesday); and weekly initial jobless claims and leading economic indicators for June (Thursday).
